                    <h5>Additional media created for the association:</h5>
                    <p>These are some of the videos created for marketing purposes. They are intentionally a bit unpolished, with the aim to make them more authentic, and for the respect of the members in the clips not wanting to have a camera and lights in their face while working out. It is also a way of shoeing the viewers how the sessions actually are in real life and what they could expect when visiting the dojo.</p>

